snippet.title: Hyper Ultra Astronautics gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Hyper Ultra Astronautics is an intense physics-based space shoot'em up for 1-16 players on the same PC. More information and downloads: http://www.fractilegames.com/astronautics/

The game development is currently in public beta phase (all major features implemented).

Trailer music by DavilOne: https://soundcloud.com/davilone
